<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Ka gelzo puoi, Pathien lungsiet,
 Mak kei ding a lang chu;
 Taklo kei tawbang hi Amah,
 A dinga ei deih chu.

[V2]
 Himahleh &quot;Ka ginchak chuh ka he'i,&quot;
 A hihthei hi tih chien takin ka he'i;
 Amah ka vawpsak zieni a,
 Dinga a vawpphat theih chu.&quot;

[V3]
 2. Ka gelzo puoi hinna dinga,
 Ginna ei piek zie chuh;
 Amah gin zieka lunga muon-
 Na hungum dan chu tawh.

[V4]
 3. Ka gelzo puoi, migilo lung,
 A Thagau nasep zie;
 Thu chun Isu a hih langa,
 Amah ginna a bawl.

[V5]
 4. A siet aphat ka hezo puoi,
 Kei ding a kikawih chuh!
 Dahna ahim, nawpna ahim,
 A maia ka muh ding?

[V6]
 5. Ka Lalpa hungphat ding bangtik,
 Ahih ka hezo puoi;
 Ka na thi man dem, hing in &quot;Van-
 Ah Amah ka tuok dem?&quot;</lyrics>
<title>I KNOW WHOM I HAVE BELIEVED</title>
<hymn_number>77</hymn_number>
</song>